    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>General term applied to many of the 40 species of glossy black birds in the genus Covus, although some birds in this genus are called "ravens"  rather than crows.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
